title: 2012 Democratic Party presidential candidates
data: Filed with the FEC to run for president on December 12 , 2011 . Paid $ 2,500 to appear on the Oklahoma ballot . Finished third with 13.79 percent in Oklahoma , qualifying him for three delegates , which the Oklahoma Democratic Party stripped due to his lack of a delegate slate
Paid $ 1,000 to appear on the New Hampshire ballot . Participated in the lesser-known candidates forum Finished second among ballot candidates in New Hampshire with 1.56 percent
